name: Salvatore Ganacci
description: '''Emir Kobilić''' ({{IPA|bs|ěmir kôbilit͡ɕ}}), known professionally as '''Salvatore Ganacci''' ({{IPA|it|salvaˈtoːre ɡaˈnattʃi|lang}}), is a Bosnian-Swedish [[Disc jockey|DJ]] and [[record producer]]. His performances at [[Tomorrowland (festival)|Tomorrowland]] in 2018 and 2019 became viral.
